      • lookupRaw

        public List<String> lookupRaw​(String key)
                       throws DictionaryException
        Dictionary method - Looks up a key and provides all possible matches, in their raw representation for dictionary editing.

        The implementation returns the result of lookup(String), but if an implementor wants to return a marked-up version of entry definitions for the purposes of allowing the user to accurately edit the dictionary, this method can be overridden.

        Specified by:
        lookupRaw in interface Dictionary
